&lt;p&gt;
Series ARX20, piston type regulator, is compatible with a primary supply pressure of 2.0MPa and is ideal for pressure adjustment of air blowing applications.  The ARX has a compact design with a width of 35mm and an overall length of 80mm.  The piston operated design ensures long operating life.  The ARX has an easy-to-operate adjustment handle.    
&lt;/p&gt;
